node.text:
He is tall, he is strong, he is handsome, and he is very smart. Thank God he takes after me. 😂🤣☺️
🎥: @tracyguns 👊🏻
.
Mom is timeless and absolutely gorgeous. She’s lean, she has strong legs, strong core, and has a tremendous amount of functional strength. A genetically gifted strong foundation. 
.
Dad has grip strength, high density bone structure, height, and a splash of Lilly White easily sunburnt skin.  Which I’m being told is an advantage. 
😂😂😂😂
.
He’s getting so smart. He’s getting so strong. He’s so protective. He has a very large heart, he’s game, and he’s making us all so proud. 
.
It’s not your birthday. Just taking a moment to give credit where credit is due. That being said. We are all very, very, proud of you.  @jaedenbaldwin

node.text:
His heart was full of love, he was dangerous, he was a guardian, he was always happy to see us and he was one of the few dogs that actually smiled to show us he loved us.
.
I tried really hard to bring him back. I’m gonna miss that smile. Might need a minute. 
.
Thank you to everyone whom showed Rambo love over the years. He loved you back. 
.
No matter what challenges you face, keep going. Take a minute to process, and then put one foot in front of the other knowing how strong you’ll be on the other side of it. 
.
Tough few days for me. Better days ahead. Continuing the journey. 
.
Seriously, everyone that showed him love. Thank you. It meant the world to him. 
.
Stay strong. 🙏🏻

node.text:
13 candles 🎂.
.
Today has me stumped. This one is tough. But I will say this. 
.
I’ve always loved racing. That being said, all the accomplishments, all the race wins, all the Championships, and every goal reached, you were the driving force behind it. None of it would be possible if you weren’t here watching.
.
Why?
.
I wanted you to think I was cool. 
.
Happy Birthday Jaeden 🎂

node.text:
Group therapy cross training with 10mm
.
Bigger holes, more velocity, more tissue damage and quite a bit more powerful than 45 auto, 40. Cal, and 9mm. 
.
Most 10mm ammunition is over twice as powerful as 9mm. At a cost. As you can see here it’s harder to shoot fast because the substantial increase in recoil makes it more difficult to control. 
.
10mm auto was originally endorsed and developed by Marine Lieutenant Jeff Cooper in 1986 after the Miami Dade gunfight. It was then adopted by the FBI for a short period before being decommissioned due to excessive recoil. Now it is exclusively used by the FBI’s hostage rescue team. Today’s FBI Agents and most law enforcement agencies use 9mm. 
.
Current usage, Deer hunting and wilderness defense against large predators. Mainly Black Bears and Grizzly bears and moose. Of which flat nose 10mm will zip right through. 
.
9mm 250 - 440 ftlbs energy
10mm 560 - 1000 ftlbs energy
.
Any 10mm auto fans out there?

node.text:
Working mermaid security detail yesterday for @zozobaldwin fifth birthday party. 🎂☺️
.
Without question, yesterday was the happiest day I’ve had in my life. 
.
Because of over the ë.
.
I love you. More than you will ever know. A volume of love you will never be able to comprehend. 
.
I’ll be here for both of you. Always. Forever. For the remainder of my life and we’ll beyond my last breath. 🙂 
. 
Until the end of time. 💕
💚🌎💚🌎

node.text:
He is tall, he is strong, he is handsome, and he is very smart. Thank God he takes after me. 😂🤣☺️
🎥: @tracyguns 👊🏻
.
Mom is timeless and absolutely gorgeous. She’s lean, she has strong legs, strong core, and has a tremendous amount of functional strength. A genetically gifted strong foundation. 
.
Dad has grip strength, high density bone structure, height, and a splash of Lilly White easily sunburnt skin.  Which I’m being told is an advantage. 
😂😂😂😂
.
He’s getting so smart. He’s getting so strong. He’s so protective. He has a very large heart, he’s game, and he’s making us all so proud. 
.
It’s not your birthday. Just taking a moment to give credit where credit is due. That being said. We are all very, very, proud of you.  @jaedenbaldwin
